A disambig ordinal list consists of two or more ordinal words separated by noun phrase conjunctions. Note that there is a minimum of two entries in the list. `grammar `[`disambigOrdinalList`](../object/disambigOrdinalList.html)`(tail)`` :   `[`DisambigOrdProd`](../object/DisambigOrdProd.html)
